msgstr "diaktifkan"

msgid "deactivated"
msgstr "dinonaktifkan"

msgid "Bulk create or update manual rates"
msgstr "Buat atau perbarui tingkat manual secara massal"

msgid ""
"Create or update multiple manual exchange rates in a single request. Each "
"rate is identified by its base_currency + target_currency pair. If a rate "
"for the pair already exists, it is updated; otherwise a new one is created. "
"Maximum 100 rates per request.\n"
"\n"
"**Request body example:**\n"
"```json\n"
"{\n"
"  \"rates\": [\n"
"    {\"base_currency\": \"USD\", \"target_currency\": \"EUR\", \"rate\": "
"\"0.92\"},\n"
"    {\"base_currency\": \"USD\", \"target_currency\": \"GBP\", \"rate\": "
"\"0.79\", \"is_active\": true}\n"
"  ]\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"Buat atau perbarui beberapa tingkat pertukaran manual dalam satu permintaan. "
"Setiap tingkat diidentifikasi oleh pasangan base_currency + target_currency-"
"nya. Jika tingkat untuk pasangan tersebut sudah ada, maka akan diperbarui; "
"jika tidak, satu yang baru akan dibuat. Maksimal 100 tingkat per permintaan. "
"**Contoh tubuh permintaan:** ```json {\n"
"  \"rates\": [\n"
"    {\"base_currency\": \"USD\", \"target_currency\": \"EUR\", \"rate\": "
"\"0.92\"},\n"
"    {\"base_currency\": \"USD\", \"target_currency\": \"GBP\", \"rate\": "
"\"0.79\", \"is_active\": true}\n"
"  ]\n"
"} ```"

msgid "Bulk operation completed"
msgstr "Operasi batch selesai"

msgid "Invalid request data."
msgstr "Data permintaan tidak valid."

msgid "base_currency, target_currency, and rate are required."
msgstr "base_currency, target_currency, dan rate diperlukan."

msgid "Base and target currencies must be different."
msgstr "Mata uang dasar dan target harus berbeda."

msgid "Exchange rate must be greater than zero."
msgstr "Tingkat pertukaran harus lebih besar dari nol."

msgid "Invalid rate value."
msgstr "Nilai tingkat tidak valid."

