msgid "Follow these steps to connect your exchange rate provider account"
msgstr ""
"Ikuti langkah-langkah berikut untuk menghubungkan akun penyedia kurs valuta "
"asing Anda"

msgid "Select Provider"
msgstr "Pilih Pemasok"

msgid "Setup Instructions"
msgstr "Instruksi Pengaturan"

msgid "Enter Credentials"
msgstr "Masukkan Kredensial"

msgid "Test Connection"
msgstr "Uji Koneksi"

msgid "Select an Exchange Rate Provider"
msgstr "Pilih Penyedia Tingkat Tukar"

msgid "Choose the exchange rate provider you want to connect to your store."
msgstr ""
"Pilih penyedia kurs valuta asing yang ingin Anda hubungkan ke toko Anda."

msgid "No exchange rate provider components are currently installed."
msgstr "Tidak ada komponen penyedia kurs valuta asing yang saat ini terinstal."

msgid ""
"Please download and install exchange rate provider components from the "
"component registry."
msgstr ""
"Silakan unduh dan instal komponen penyedia kurs valuta asing dari registri "
"komponen."

msgid "Browse Components"
msgstr "Lihat Komponen"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Batal"

msgid "Next"
msgstr "Berikutnya"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Before entering credentials, review these setup steps for "
"%(provider)s.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Sebelum memasukkan kredensial, tinjau langkah-langkah pengaturan "
"berikut untuk %(provider)s.\n"
"        "

msgid "Setup Instructions Not Available"
msgstr "Instruksi Pengaturan Tidak Tersedia"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    Setup instructions are not available for this version of "
"%(provider)s.\n"
"                    Please contact support for assistance or check for an "
"updated version.\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                    Instruksi pengaturan tidak tersedia untuk versi "
"%(provider)s ini. Silakan hubungi dukungan untuk bantuan atau periksa versi "
"terbaru.\n"
"                    "

msgid "Back"
msgstr "Kembali"

msgid "Continue to Credentials"
msgstr "Lanjut ke Kredensial"

msgid "Enter API Credentials"
msgstr "Masukkan Kredensial API"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Enter your API credentials for %(provider)s. These will be securely "
"encrypted and stored.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Masukkan kredensial API untuk %(provider)s. Kredensial ini akan "
"dienkripsi dan disimpan secara aman.\n"
"        "

msgid "Don't have an account yet?"
msgstr "Belum memiliki akun?"

msgid "You'll need an account to get API credentials."
msgstr "Anda memerlukan akun untuk mendapatkan kredensial API."

msgid "Sign up here"
msgstr "Daftar di sini"

msgid "API Credentials"
msgstr "Kredensial API"

msgid "Select..."
msgstr "Pilih..."

msgid "No credential fields configured for this provider."
msgstr "Tidak ada bidang kredensial yang dikonfigurasikan untuk penyedia ini."

msgid ""
"Your credentials will be encrypted using AES-256 encryption before being "
"stored in the database."
msgstr ""
"Kredensial Anda akan dienkripsi menggunakan enkripsi AES-256 sebelum "
"disimpan di database."

#, python-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Test the connection to %(provider)s to verify your credentials are "
"correct.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Uji koneksi ke %(provider)s untuk memverifikasi apakah kredensial "
"Anda benar.\n"
"        "

msgid "Testing connection..."
msgstr "Menguji koneksi..."

msgid "Please wait while we verify your credentials."
msgstr "Silakan tunggu sementara kami memverifikasi kredensial Anda."

msgid "Click to test the connection with your entered credentials."
msgstr "Klik untuk menguji koneksi dengan kredensial yang Anda masukkan."

msgid "Connection Successful!"
msgstr "Koneksi Berhasil!"

msgid "Connection Details"
msgstr "Detail Koneksi"

msgid "Save & Finish"
msgstr "Simpan & Selesai"

msgid "Your credentials were verified successfully."
msgstr "Kredensial Anda telah diverifikasi dengan sukses."

msgid "Connection Failed"
msgstr "Koneksi Gagal"

msgid "Could not connect to the provider API."
msgstr "Tidak dapat terhubung ke API penyedia."

msgid "An unexpected error occurred."
msgstr "Terjadi kesalahan tak terduga."

